{"tid":34171,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"忍無可忍！華倫西亞球迷怒圍球隊基地聲討球隊","createTime":"2016-12-11T10:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T12:27:19.000Z","uid":18669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5e3445c8982143b49cd5321c5cf0f2fab90eee","tid":34171,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:24:55.000Z","msg":"今天在聯賽中華倫西亞客場2-3負于皇家蘇斯達，聯賽中已經連續7場比賽未嘗勝績，在積分榜上已經非常接近落入降級區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華倫西亞球迷已經對於球隊的表現忍無可忍了，在上一場主場被馬拉加逼平之後，梅斯塔亞球場就爆發出陣陣噓聲。本輪球隊再次輸球，憤怒的華倫西亞球迷決定用行動表達對球隊的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n當華倫西亞球員從聖塞巴斯蒂安回到華倫西亞之後，約100名華倫西亞亞球迷將華倫西亞基地圍了個水洩不通，他們高呼聲討球隊的口號，質問球隊為什麼成績如此糟糕。由於憤怒的球迷圍堵了基地，華倫西亞球員無法回家，俱樂部無奈只得報警。據目擊者稱，部分球迷試圖打開華倫西亞球隊大巴的車門向球隊討要說法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在警方的幫助下，華倫西亞球員已經安全離開了球隊基地。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48feba2a3ee95e2cbbc8250e7a61bb872b78960","tid":34171,"uid":41575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"降班啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35c1ec1ed39f85e2b65505cd479fbcacbb02de2","tid":34171,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0825afdfe7d12715f14bc9023abfec0a307c2ed3","tid":34171,"uid":13088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>降班啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最衰都係你 打咁好做咩"},{"pid":"7516a6fdbe21a4e6e2039f8d09a5d37f1e2a69f0","tid":34171,"uid":41575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>降班啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"